1959;;The Bandit of Zhobe;;British;;John Gilling;;Victor Mature, Anne Aubrey;;adventure;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Bandit_of_Zhobe;;A bandit with a price on his head, is seen this time blind for revenge. He thinks that the British have massacred his people, his family, his wife and child. But he is wrong. Only the little romantic daughter of his enemy, overflowing with pity for him, could open his eyes to the truth. [3]